  0070            ************************************************************
  0071            * Register usage
  0072            * R0-R3   General purpose registers
  0073            * R4-R8   Temporary registers
  0074            * R9      Stack pointer
  0075            * R10     Highest slot in use + Timer counter
  0076            * R11     Subroutine return address
  0077            * R12     Configuration register
  0078            * R13     Copy of VDP status byte and counter for sound play
  0079            * R14     Copy of VDP register #0 and VDP register #1 bytes
  0080            * R15     VDP read/write address
  0081            ************************************************************
  0082            * Workspace and register equates
  0083            ********@*****@*********************@***********************
