  2010            
  2011            * VIRTKB () ..:
  2012            ************************************************************
  2013            * VIRTKB - Read virtual keyboard and joysticks
  2014            ************************************************************
  2015            *  BL @VIRTKB
  2016            *-----------------------------------------------------------
  2017            *  COLUMN     0     1  2  3  4  5    6   7
  2018            *         +---------------------------------+------+
  2019            *  ROW 7  |   =     .  ,  M  N  /   JS1 JS2 | Fire |
  2020            *  ROW 6  | SPACE   L  K  J  H  :;  JS1 JS2 | Left |
  2021            *  ROW 5  | ENTER   O  I  U  Y  P   JS1 JS2 | Right|
  2022            *  ROW 4  |         9  8  7  6  0   JS1 JS2 | Down |
  2023            *  ROW 3  | FCTN    2  3  4  5  1   JS1 JS2 | Up   |
  2024            *  ROW 2  | SHIFT   S  D  F  G  A           +------|
  2025            *  ROW 1  | CTRL    W  E  R  T  Q                  |
  2026            *  ROW 0  |         X  C  V  B  Z                  |
  2027            *         +----------------------------------------+
  2028            *  See MG smart programmer 1986 
  2029            *  September/Page 15 and November/Page 6
  2030            *  Also see virtual keyboard status for bits to check
  2031            *-----------------------------------------------------------
  2032            *  Register usage
  2033            *  TMP0     Keyboard matrix column to process
  2034            *  TMP1MSB  Keyboard matrix 8 bits of 1 column
  2035            *  TMP2     Virtual keyboard flags

